NUMBER 2304
NAME Jungle Clearing
JUNGLE
DAY_LIGHT
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
This clearing has been cleared out of the surrounding jungle so that a small
cottage could be built here. The cottage is a simple wooden structure that has
obviously seen better days. The door to the cottage stands open. You can see
exits from the clearing to the north and west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 2302
EXIT N 2306
EXIT ABOVE 2310
;item 0 door
ITEM 0 65 VAL2=2305 OPEN UNLOCKED
;
;
NUMBER 2305
NAME Inside cottage
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
CHANNEL 134
REGION 131
*DESCRIPTION_START
You find yourself inside a small cottage. It appears that this cottage was at
one time a neat and tidy affair set up for both work and living. A skeleton is
on the sleeping mat against the wall and it is apparent that no one alive has
been here for a long time.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2304
; ITEM 0 SKELETON
ITEM 0 390
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You see the skeleton of what appears to be a small humanoid.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CAST 0
  IFVAR SPELLNUM = 311
    CLEARVERB
    EQUAL SPELLNUM 0
    ECHO ALL You hear a wispering sigh come from the skeleton.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Suddenly a weak voice comes from the skeleton.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL "So long ... I ... waited."
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL "Sphere ... powerful ... "
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL "Dying ... hidden ... cliff"
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Suddenly the skeleton crumbles to dust as if these final words were too much.
    REMOVEITEM 0
  ENDIF
ENDIF
